Now, our shining youth begins!

7
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:06,000
ねぽらぼ学園 ☆5周年記念！！輝く学寮祭☆
Nepolabo Academy: 5th Anniversary!! The Radiant Dormitory Festival!

8
00:04:12,670 --> 00:04:18,300
今日は学寮祭。生徒会が中心になって開催する、夏の一大イベント！
Today is the Dormitory Festival. It's a huge summer event organized primarily by the student council!

9
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:23,900
会長からの頼みで、急遽ねぽらぼで出し物を考えることになったんだけど――
At the student council president's request, we had to come up with a performance for Nepolabo at the last minute, but...

10
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:27,400
