But hey, summer means the pool!
Wouldn't it be cool to do something here?

282
00:18:42,854 --> 00:18:47,454
プールでできることといえば……撮影会！！
Something we can do in the pool is... a photo shoot!!

283
00:18:47,754 --> 00:18:50,621
ねねたちの水着姿で！
In our swimsuits!

284
00:18:50,954 --> 00:18:53,721
お客さんを……悩殺♡
