In that case... let's make this an endless summer!!!

296
00:19:46,754 --> 00:19:48,954
おーーー！！
Ohhh!!

297
00:20:05,683 --> 00:20:09,083
君と夏フェス
作詞・作曲：宮崎朝子
Kimi to Natsu Fesu (You and the Summer Festival)
Lyrics/Composition: Miyazaki Asako

298
00:20:14,583 --> 00:20:19,683
まだ照れ臭いあいつとフェスに
Going to a festival with that guy I'm still shy around

299
00:20:19,683 --> 00:20:24,883
行く約束をしたはいいけど
I'm glad we made a promise to go, but

300
00:20:25,483 --> 00:20:30,583
あまりノってたら引かれそう
If I get too into it, I might turn him off

301
00:20:30,583 --> 00:20:35,883
