My sweat won't stop

307
00:21:02,583 --> 00:21:08,183
それとも君への気持ち？
Or is it my feelings for you?

308
00:21:08,183 --> 00:21:13,583
滴り落ちてく恋心
My love is dripping down

309
00:21:13,583 --> 00:21:18,583
こぼれないようにすくってね
Scoop it up so it doesn't spill

310
00:21:18,583 --> 00:21:23,583
止まらないのは夏への期待
My expectations for summer won't stop

311
00:21:23,583 --> 00:21:28,583
忘れられない夏になるかも
It might become an unforgettable summer

312
00:21:30,283 --> 00:21:35,283
夏の日差しで焼け焦げそう
I'm about to get scorched by the summer sun

313
00:21:35,283 --> 00:21:40,383
すべてがスローモーションになる
Everything turns into slow motion

314
00:21:40,883 --> 00:21:45,983
他人の汗もどうでもよくて
I don't even care about other people's sweat

315
00:21:45,983 --> 00:21:51,183
